measurements.description: Twenty-one round, flat flowers and one bud evenly arranged on one 98.5-cm arching inflorescence, eight buds on a 56-cm arching inflorescence; sepals clear yellow, dorsal sepal faint red stripe centrally; petals clear yellow; lip slightly ruffled, white, yellow distally, dark red blotches near lower margins and centrally, sidelobes overlaid yellow; column yellow, faintly blushed red, anther cap yellow; substance firm; texture matte.
